title: Hardline Trump supporters rally outside the White House | AFP
author: AFP News Agency
description:
Hardline supporters of US President Donald Trump rally outside the White House, by the Washington Monument, in DC to pressure Congress into rejecting Democrat Joe Biden's victory certification. President Trump is set to address the crowd later Wednesday.
